---
title: Mexican Turkey Stew with Tortilla Chips
description: Packed with hearty and delicious turkey and veggies, this Mexican stew is the perfect remedy to a long work week. Crushed tortilla chips and a dollop of lime crema offer a pop of flavour, perfect for finishing off this bowl of goodness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-turkey-stew-d6f86199.jpg
